description:
There's a lot going on this week in the world of Bravo and Danny is here to break it all down. First, Orange County is changing up the cast and bringing back a familiar face. Hulu debuts a documentary about Tom and Erika, plus recaps of this week's The Real Housewives of Beverly Hills and The Real Housewives of New York!


The Housewife and Hustler: 8:45ish

RHOBH Recap: 18:00ish

RHONY Recap: 39:00ish
